text: Slava Zupančič (5 July 1931 - 2 April 2000) was a Slovenian alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1956 Winter Olympics, representing Yugoslavia. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2000 deaths Category:Slovenian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Yugoslavia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Kranj
